Injector/Double Punch/Bumblebee/Manterror:

Injector nodded at Shredder's orders.  "Is that...liquidate...or clean the 
room?"

"Clean the room, I think." Manterror said.

"Dang." Injector said.  A gurgling noise was heard in his throat, hot oil 
spitting out of his mouth at Mantella face as Manterror, Bumblebee, Injector, 
and Double Punch left the room, Bumblebee yelling to Shredder.

"If you need ANY help, yell.  We'll be there to crack that roach's shell open 
so fast!"
